a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.4.6</biblScope> </bibl> (s. v.l.); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑ. τὴν ἀντωμοσίαν κατά τινος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2001.tlg026:313c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Them.\">Them.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">26.313c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bring an accusation</tr_> against one, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴπ᾽ εἴ τι καινὸν ὑπογράφῃ τὠμῷ βίῳ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg009.perseus-grc1:1118\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HF\">HF</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1118</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n108215.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">write under orders</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">from dictation,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐκ ἔχων οὐδὲ τὸν ὑπογράφοντα</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">an amanuensis,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2003.tlg013:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Jul.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">28</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg048:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Caes.\">Caes.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n108215.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\"